result.execSummary:
The defendant Ali nmi Rahimlou was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Ali nmi Rahimlou is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Ali nmi Rahimlou was found guilty of Possess w/Intent-LSD (<=1gram) [Modifiers: Penalties for Felonies-Class "G" Felony], a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1m)(f)1.
